AUDIENCE: We love Trump! We love
Trump!

28:19.798 --> 28:22.901 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP (R), Presidential
Candidate:
Oh, we love you, we love you!

28:22.935 --> 28:23.869 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
